From 331266e370cc92bb2a2880902b195b13a8ef7466 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>
Date: Thu, 8 Jan 2026 01:19:04 +0100
Subject: [PATCH 2/8] arm: gxp: add HPE GXP SoC platform support

Add platform support for the HPE GXP SoC used in HPE ProLiant BMCs.

SoC drivers added:
- gxp-xreg: Extended register GPIO for LEDs, fans, PSUs, and system control
- gxp-fn2: Embedded management processor support
- gxp-csm: Slave instrumentation and system support
- gxp-chif: Channel interface for host communication
- gxp-cpu: CPU presence interface
- gxp-dbg: Host debug POST code capture
- gxp-srom: System ROM offset configuration
- gxp-v-eeprom: Virtual EEPROM support

Also includes updates to the base device tree (gxp.dts) and ARM machine
code (gxp.c).

Signed-off-by: Marcello Sylvester Bauer <marcello.bauer@9elements.com>

